          ],
          "name": "Hefty Defense",
          "subtype": "ability",
          "text": "A murajau's weight and legs make them incredibly difficult to trip or be moved unwillingly. They can be tripped only by creatures of their size or larger and have a +2 circumstance bonus to all defenses against being shoved or tripped. However, a murajau can Stand only as a 2-action activity.",
